desc_long								关于这款游戏							Color Chemistry is an abstract color mixing puzzle game.The game includes 42 colorful brain teasing puzzles!The mechanics of the game is based on the modern theory of color. Additive and subtractive color combinations are used.Your task is to solve a puzzle in optimal number of steps.KEY FEATURESUnique puzzle game mechanicsPeaceful puzzling atmosphere42 puzzles22 Steam AchievementsTrading cardsColor randomness of puzzle piecesThe game is for everyone - there is no age restriction content						
